{"TopicId":181787,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Offset controls on console","CreatedByName":"Jebediah Kerman Jr.","CreatedById":189524,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-01-28T21:35:45Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Jebediah Kerman Jr.","CreatedById":189524,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-01-28T21:35:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow would I switch between relative and absolute offset on an Xbox one?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks in advance!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-01-28T21:35:56Z\u0022 title=\u002201/28/2019 09:35  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 28, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Jebediah Kerman Jr.\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-01-28T22:29:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhich preset are you using?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jebediah Kerman Jr.","CreatedById":189524,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-01-29T11:22:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRadial Preset.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-01-29T15:31:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUm, as I recall, that was one of the few editor functions that never got implemented in Radial preset. I don\u0027t know what the current status of that is, though. If you file it as a bug report on the tracker, that may help it get implemented.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHowever, if you momentarily switch into Enhanced preset -- then the X button should toggle the mode, and you can do your edit, and then switch back to radial preset.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-01-29T15:39:03Z\u0022 title=\u002201/29/2019 03:39  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 29, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by bewing\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jebediah Kerman Jr.","CreatedById":189524,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-01-29T19:16:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOkay, thanks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jebediah Kerman Jr.","CreatedById":189524,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-01-30T20:32:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWait, the only presets are cursor, radial, and simplified?!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"bewing","CreatedById":154251,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-01-31T01:21:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223531745\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022181787\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221548880339\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022189524\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jebediah Kerman Jr.\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, Jebediah Kerman Jr. said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWait, the only presets are cursor, radial, and simplified?!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, sorry, I meant \u0022simplified\u0022 -- the names changed a couple times and I forgot the final one selected.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jebediah Kerman Jr.","CreatedById":189524,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-02-02T14:50:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh, thanks.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}